summary: Finally saw Detective Pikachu! It was soooo goooooddddd! Like I went into it knowing it was good, and I knew all of the Pokemon...
question: Finally saw Detective Pikachu! It was soooo goooooddddd! Like I went into it knowing it was good, and I knew all of the Pokemon looked amazing. But everything was so well done??? The music and the lighting just aaaaah
answer: YES!!!!!!!!!!! i was freaking OUT when i went to go see it in theaters. it was so so so good……i cant wait for more pokemon movies…theres so much potential….move over mcu, make way for the pcu (pokemon cinematic universe)
